Required Editions and User Permissions:

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Group, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

User Permissions Needed:
Create and Customize Reports or Report Builder to add a unique count to a report

When adding a unique count to a column, it shows the number of unique column values. Duplicate values arenâ€™t counted.

Each report supports up to three unique counts.
Lightning table dashboard widgets don't support unique counts.
Fields of certain data types don't support unique counts:
Blobs
Clobs
Encrypted fields
Multi-select picklist
Text area
